Peru names and spatial

Source: R/data.R
Peru.Rd

A dataset containing the names of the 1874 districts, 196 provinces and 25 departments of Peru according INEI - 2017, additionally also is the limits administrative level 3 in a spatial vector format.

Usage

data(Peru)

Format

A dataset with 1874 rows and 9 variables:

ubigeo

Code of six numbers for each district

dep.code

Code to each departament

dep

Name of each departament

prov.code

Code to each province

prov

Name of each province

distr.code

Code to each district

distr

Name of each district

capital

Name of the capital main

Source

https://www.inei.gob.pe/
